      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission delivering power to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, mitigating common floor-pan fatigue associated with this platform. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the high-pressure double-VANOS system operates within factory tolerances. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with regular use, the mechanical integrity is prioritized, offering precise turn-in and exceptional feedback for the discerning purist.",
